                <div class="title-text">Privacy Policy of Chatty</div>
                <p><strong>Last Updated: Oct. 15, 2016</strong></p>
                <p>* in the below, calls "you or your authorized child" as "User".
                <p>Protecting User's privacy is really important to us (“<strong>Chatty</strong>,” “<strong>we</strong>,” “<strong>our</strong>,” or “<strong>us</strong>”).
                    With this in mind, we’re providing this Privacy Policy to explain our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information
                    that we receive through our services (Chatty, chatting services), which are accessible via Facebook Messenger.
                    Our website is located at <a href="https://www.chatty.top/">https://www.chatty.top</a>.
                    This Privacy Policy does not apply to any third party websites, services, or applications, even if they are accessible through any of our Services.</p>
                <p><strong>1. REVISIONS TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY</strong></p>
                <p><strong>ANY INFORMATION THAT IS COLLECTED VIA OUR SERVICES IS COVERED BY THE PRIVACY POLICY IN EFFECT AT THE TIME SUCH INFORMATION IS COLLECTED.
                    WE MAY REVISE THIS PRIVACY POLICY FROM TIME TO TIME. IF WE MAKE ANY MATERIAL CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY,
                    INCLUDING ANY CHANGE THAT WE PROPOSE THAT WILL HAVE RETROACTIVE EFFECT,
                    WE’LL NOTIFY YOU OF THOSE CHANGES BY POSTING THEM ON OUR WEBSITE.</strong></p>
                <p><strong>2. COLLECTION AND USE OF INFORMATION</strong></p>
                <p>a. <span class="underline">Information Collected or Received from User</span>.</p>
                <p>Our primary goals in collecting information are to provide and improve our Services,
                    to administer User's use of the Services,
                    and to enable User to enjoy and easily navigate our Services.</p>
                <p>Our services are under the service of Facebook and/or Facebook Messenger and/or Facebook Messenger Platform,
                    so User must have accepted those conditions (e.g. Privacy Policy, Terms of Conditions, etc.).
                    Our services is under Facebook Messenger Platform directly, and only in there,
                    and then there is no directly connection to/from the outside at all.</p>
                <p>i. <span class="underline">Account Information</span>.</p>
                <p>During using our services, we use your account information of Facebook and/or Facebook Messenger and/or Facebook Messenger Platform.
                    We just use the information to provide our services only.</p>
                <p>ii. <span class="underline">Chatting Information</span>.</p>
                <p>During chatting on our services, we will NOT collect any messages you send, just transfering them to your chat mate only.
                    Exclude of the case to debug or improve our services, to use it for debugging or improvement purpose only.</p>

                <p>b. <span class="underline"> Information Collected Using Cookies and other Web Technologies </span>.</p>
                <p>Like many website owners and operators, we use automated data collection tools such as Cookies and Web Beacons to collect certain information on our services.</p>
                <p>“<strong>Cookies</strong>” are small text files that are placed on your hard drive by a Web server when User access our Services.
                    We may NOT use neither session information nor cookies DIRECTLY although,
                    Facebook services may possiblly to use session Cookies and/or persistent Cookies to identify that User have logged in
                    to the Services and to tell us how and when User interact with our Services.
                    We just use the information from Facebook Messenger Platform only.
                    We may also possiblly to use the information to aggregate statistical information.</p>

                <p>c. <span class="underline"> Information Related to Use of the Services</span>.</p>
                <p>Our servers automatically record certain information about how a person uses our Services (we refer to this information as “<strong>Log Data</strong>”),
                    Log Data may include information such as a account ID, accessing time, etc.
                    We use the Log Data for improvement or debugging our services only.
                    We do NOT aggregate private information such as your conversation although,
                    we may possiblly to aggregate statistical information such as chatting language, time, etc., without identifical information.</p>

                <p><strong>3. THE SECURITY OF YOUR INFORMATION</strong></p>
                <p>We take appropriate administrative, physical, and electronic measures designed to protect the information that we collect from or about User
                    from accidental or unlawful destruction, accidental loss or unauthorized access, use, modification, interference, or disclosure.
                    Please be aware, however, that no method of transmitting information over the Internet or storing information is completely secure.
                    Accordingly, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of any information.</p>

                <p><strong>4. LINKS TO OTHER SITES</strong></p>
                <p>Our Services may contain links to websites and services that are owned or operated by third parties (each, a “<strong>Third Party Service</strong>”).
                    Any information that User provide on or to a Third Party Service or that is collected
                    by a Third Party Service (including Google, Facebook) is provided directly to the owner or operator of the Third Party Service
                    and is subject to the owner’s or operator’s privacy policy.
                    We’re not responsible for the content, privacy, or security practices and policies of any Third Party Service.
                    To protect User's information we recommend that you carefully review the privacy policies of all Third Party Service
                    that User access via our Services.</p>

                <p><strong>5. TRACKING</strong></p>
                <p>If we need to track the bad mannered, illegal in law, or etc., possiblly to track / trace the ID or information of the ID to investigate.
                    This is for our services to keep it better, and to avoid bad feelings for you also.</p>

                <p><strong>6. Questions</strong></p>
                <p>Please contact us to <a href="mailto:chattyfbm@gmail.com">chattyfbm@gmail.com</a> if you have any questions about our Privacy Policy.</p>

                <p><strong>7. Emails</strong></p>
                <p>Emails or any communication to us will be possiblly to store, record or collect for answer to you or for solve the problem although,
                    we do NOT use the information for any other kind of purpose. And then we keep mind to do not leak any bit of them.</p>
